about:
As day turns to night and night turns to day in this endless cycle, the Seasons collection represents those special moments suspended in time, whether its in peaceful solitude or with the ones you love. This collection is a series of NFTs based around the four seasons  Summer, Autumn, Winter, & Spring.

The four collections will feature 16 images, each with 2 phases, exclusively designed for this series by the inspirational artist DirtyRobot. Each image will be time-based, evolving through a series of phases, depending on the time of day it is.

For more details: [https://dirtyrobot.com](https://dirtyrobot.com)
